data.description: Walk to SouthPark restaurants, Harris Teeter, fitness center, and more. Great location for this 1 bedroom, upstairs condo. Brand new vinyl plank flooring. Recently replaced HVAC and furnace with Nest Thermostat for low electric bills. Spacious bedroom has 2 large closets. Large living room and dining area. Large closet. HOA recently announced it is FHA approved.
